originalText.text:
The staff, technicians and Doctor Pagano were excellent! Professional caring, courteous, kind and positive, during my exam.  Doctor Pagano was easy to talk with as well as kind in his bedside manner.  I truly never felt talked down too by him and his down to earth approach was actually a breath of fresh air. I understood everything he said and he was very relatable.  A calm demeanor.  Thanks Doctor Pagano it was a pleasure.

Paul T.
